Usage:

./mvsctl -s, --starts        starts the server on port 80 (needs root permission)

./mvsctl -x, --stop         stops the server (needs root permission)

./mvsctl -d, --devel        starts the server in development mode on port 8080

./mvsctl -c, --change PATH  changes the location of the movie directory to the specified PATH	


Tested Browsers:

- Google Chrome
- Chromium
- Opera
- Firefox
- Safari
- iOS browser
- Android browser
